Dialogue: 0,00:01:03.40,00:01:06.91,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 愛しあうことも
Dialogue: 0,00:01:06.91,00:01:09.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 終わりはしない
Dialogue: 0,00:01:09.92,00:01:14.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ On The Way
Dialogue: 0,00:01:14.42,00:01:17.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:01:17.93,00:01:21.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ I Wanna ROCKS
Dialogue: 0,00:01:21.94,00:01:24.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ 胸にROCKS
Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.92,00:01:36.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)ハァ ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:01:36.93,00:01:42.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:01:42.94,00:01:46.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)《ﾅﾙﾄの兄ちゃんたちだって戦ってるんだ》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.66,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Naruto y los demás están peleando!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:49.83,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Nosotros también podemos!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:48.45,00:01:50.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)《僕たちだって！》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:57.34,Cart_A_Tre,,0,0,0,,Una herramienta llamada shinobi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:55.33,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Una herramienta llamada shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:58.40,00:02:01.91,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)おじちゃん！ギイチのおじちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:00.06,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Giichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:04.01,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Giichi, ábreme!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:01.91,00:02:04.41,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ここを開けてよ！
Dialogue: 0,00:02:04.41,00:02:06.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,一緒に橋に行ってよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.81,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Ven al puente conmigo.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.42,00:02:10.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,今度こそ みんなでやればガトーたちを やっつけられるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:10.72,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Si peleamos unidos,\Npodemos vencer a Gatou!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:12.93,00:02:14.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(鍵を掛ける音)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:21.10,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Inari, abandoné la pelea hace tiempo.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:16.44,00:02:18.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｷﾞｲﾁ)イナリ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:02:18.44,00:02:21.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,わしは もう戦うことをやめたんじゃ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:02:21.45,00:02:24.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前のオヤジだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.90,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Incluso tu padre…
Dialogue: 0,00:02:24.45,00:02:27.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,英雄と呼ばれた男だって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:27.10,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Incluso nuestro héroe…
Dialogue: 0,00:02:27.46,00:02:29.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,もういない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:29.12,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Ya no está.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:33.97,00:02:35.98,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｷﾞｲﾁ)戦おうとすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:38.24,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Si peleamos, habrá más víctimas.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:35.98,00:02:38.98,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,多くの犠牲が出る｡
Dialogue: 0,00:02:38.98,00:02:43.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,大切なものはもう失いたくない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:42.45,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No quiero perder nada más.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:43.49,00:02:47.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,もう誰も後悔したくないんじゃ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:46.92,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Nadie quiere arrepentirse de nada más.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:47.50,00:02:57.51,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:03.03,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Yo tampoco quiero arrepentirme.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:58.96,00:03:03.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ぼ… 僕だって後悔したくないよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:03.46,00:03:06.47,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,だから戦わなきゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.84,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Por eso tenemos que pelear!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:06.47,00:03:11.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞ)＜男なら後悔しない生き方を選べ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:10.67,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Un hombre elige un estilo de vida\Ndel que no se arrepiente.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:13.48,00:03:15.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)僕は母ちゃんも じいちゃんも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:17.85,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Quiero mucho a mamá, al abuelo y a ti.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:15.99,00:03:17.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ギイチのおじちゃんも大好きだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:20.65,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Quiero a toda la gente de la ciudad!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:17.99,00:03:21.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,町のみんなが大好きなんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.79,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Ahora lo comprendo.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:26.51,00:03:29.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,僕 分かったんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:29.02,00:03:33.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,泣き虫のまんまじゃ何にも守れやしないんだって｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:35.20,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Ahora sé que llorando\Nno se defiende nada.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:33.02,00:03:36.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,もう分かったんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:36.03,00:03:46.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:03:53.00,00:03:58.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｱｶﾞﾘ)イナリは 立派な男になったね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:57.94,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Inari se volvió un gran hombre.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:00.01,00:04:02.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｱｶﾞﾘ)いいのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:04.75,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿De verdad vas a dejar que vaya solo?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:02.02,00:04:05.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,イナリをこのまま一人で行かせて｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:10.53,00:04:13.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)開けてよ！ ねぇ！(ﾉｯｸ)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.93,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Abran, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:13.54,00:04:17.55,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)お願いだよ 一緒に戦ってよ｡(ﾉｯｸ)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.64,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor, peleen conmigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:20.34,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Escúchame, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,00:04:17.55,00:04:21.55,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)おじさん 僕の話を聞いて！(ﾉｯｸ)
Dialogue: 0,00:04:21.55,00:04:25.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:25.56,00:04:28.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,どうして…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:31.12,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Por qué?\N¿Por qué nadie me abre la puerta?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:28.07,00:04:32.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,どうして誰も扉を開けてくれないんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.24,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Eres fuerte.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:36.08,00:04:39.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾅﾙﾄ)＜お前は強ぇよ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:04:39.59,00:04:44.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)《ナルトの兄ちゃん…》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:42.23,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,00:04:44.10,00:04:48.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:50.61,00:05:00.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(忍犬たちのうなり声)
Dialogue: 0,00:05:00.57,00:05:05.07,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)再不斬少し はしゃぎ過ぎたな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.32,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Zabuza, quisiste divertirte\Nmás de lo que debías.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:05.07,00:05:08.08,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前の野望は大きすぎた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.49,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Tu ambición era demasiado grande.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:10.59,00:05:12.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)水影暗殺｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:15.09,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Un intento fallido de golpe de Estado\Ny asesinato del Mizukage.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:12.59,00:05:15.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そして クーデター失敗｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:15.60,00:05:19.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,数人の部下と共に野に下り
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:21.10,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Escapaste con varios esbirros\Ny te convertiste en fugitivo.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:19.10,00:05:21.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,抜け忍となった男｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:25.94,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Tu nombre no tardó en llegar a Konoha.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:21.61,00:05:26.62,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前の名前は すぐに木ノ葉の里にも伝えられたよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:28.74,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Acumulabas dinero para vengarte
Dialogue: 0,00:05:26.62,00:05:29.12,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,報復のための資金作り｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:32.74,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,y esperabas escapar\Nde los rastreadores que te buscan.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:29.12,00:05:33.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そして 追い忍の捜索と報復から逃れるため｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:33.13,00:05:35.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなところだろう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:38.92,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Imagino que por eso trabajabas\Npara una alimaña como Gatou.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:35.13,00:05:39.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前が ガトーのような害虫に くみしたのは…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:39.14,00:05:42.15,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,再不斬 お前はこの俺が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:44.88,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Zabuza, ¿crees que el Sharingan\Nes mi único truco?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:42.15,00:05:46.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,写輪眼だけで生きてきたと思うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.52,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Esta vez no usaré una copia.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:46.16,00:05:48.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,今度はコピーじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:53.93,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Te mostraré una técnica propia.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:48.66,00:05:52.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺自身の術を…
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.10,00:05:54.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,披露してやる｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:54.61,00:06:04.62,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:06:04.63,00:06:07.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)うぉ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.38,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Raikiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.38,Naruto_Nota,,0,0,0,,Cortador de Relámpago
Dialogue: 0,00:06:07.13,00:06:09.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,雷切！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:14.15,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Qué…? Hay tanto chakra\Nen su mano que puede verse.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:09.14,00:06:11.64,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)《な… 何だ？ チャクラが
Dialogue: 0,00:06:11.64,00:06:15.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,手に… 目に見えるほどに》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.28,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Eres demasiado peligroso.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:16.65,00:06:19.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)お前は危険すぎる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:24.49,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Tazuna-san, al que intentas matar,\Nes un símbolo de valor para este país.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:19.66,00:06:22.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前が殺そうとしているタズナさんは
Dialogue: 0,00:06:22.66,00:06:24.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,この国の勇気だ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:24.67,00:06:27.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,タズナさんの架ける橋は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:28.90,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,El puente que construye\Nes la esperanza del país.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:27.17,00:06:29.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,この国の希望だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.30,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Tu ambición sacrifica a demasiada gente.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:29.18,00:06:32.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前の野望は多くの人を犠牲にする｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:32.68,00:06:34.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そういうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:37.24,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No es propio de un shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:34.69,00:06:37.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,忍のやることじゃないんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:38.71,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No me importa.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:37.69,00:06:40.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)知るか｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:40.20,00:06:45.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は 俺の理想のために戦ってきた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:44.88,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Peleo para cumplir mis ideales.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:45.21,00:06:47.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そして それは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:49.16,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Y seguiré haciéndolo.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:47.21,00:06:49.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,これからも変わらん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.09,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Te lo repetiré.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:52.66,00:06:56.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)もう一度 言う｡(再不斬)あぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.29,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Ríndete.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:56.16,00:06:58.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)諦めろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:04.20,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,En tu futuro solo veo muerte.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:00.67,00:07:04.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)お前の未来は 死だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:15.14,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Naruto-kun. Mátame, por favor.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:12.20,00:07:16.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(白)ナルト君僕を殺してください｡
Dialogue: 0,00:07:18.71,00:07:21.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(白)さぁ 早く｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:20.78,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, hazlo.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:25.22,00:07:28.72,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何を ちゅうちょしているんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.72,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Por qué dudas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:33.20,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡No lo entiendo!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:31.73,00:07:33.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,納得いかねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:38.68,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Es que ser fuerte\Nes la única razón que tienes para vivir?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:33.74,00:07:35.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,強ぇヤツでいるってことだけが
Dialogue: 0,00:07:35.74,00:07:39.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前が この世にいていい理由なのかよ!?
Dialogue: 0,00:07:41.25,00:07:45.26,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,戦う以外でだってよほかの何かで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:47.61,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Puedes hacer que te reconozcan\Nde otras maneras.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:45.26,00:07:48.77,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,自分を認めさせりゃよかったはずだろ？
Dialogue: 0,00:07:48.77,00:07:51.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,君と森で会った日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:55.22,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,El día que te vi en el bosque\Npensé que nos parecíamos.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:51.21,00:07:53.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,君は僕と似ていると
Dialogue: 0,00:07:53.71,00:07:56.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そう思いました｡
Dialogue: 0,00:07:57.72,00:08:01.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,君にも分かるはずです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:08:00.38,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Deberías comprenderlo.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:01.73,00:08:07.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,君の手を汚させることになってすみません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:06.36,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Siento que tengas\Nque ensuciarte las manos por mí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:12.19,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿No hay otra solución?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:07.24,00:08:09.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それしか…
Dialogue: 0,00:08:09.74,00:08:13.75,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それしか方法はねえのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.66,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:13.75,00:08:15.75,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,はい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:23.88,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,En otras circunstancias\Nhabríamos podido ser amigos.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:18.76,00:08:22.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前とは ほかの所で会ってたら
Dialogue: 0,00:08:22.27,00:08:25.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,友達になれたかもな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:35.06,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Espero que logres cumplir tu sueño.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:30.79,00:08:35.80,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(白)《君は夢をつかみ取ってください》
Dialogue: 0,00:08:35.80,00:08:38.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《あいつにも…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.06,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Él también…
Dialogue: 0,00:08:38.30,00:08:42.80,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケにも 夢があったんだ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:42.50,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Sasuke también tenía un sueño.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:45.82,00:08:47.82,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,はあー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.78,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Gracias.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:50.32,00:08:54.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(白)《ありがとう 君は強くなる》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.94,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Te harás fuerte.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:59.91,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,La niebla empieza a dispersarse.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:56.27,00:09:01.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾀｽﾞﾅ)おぉ 超濃かった霧がだんだん晴れてきたぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.12,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Están cara a cara ahí.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:02.78,00:09:05.29,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｻｸﾗ)あそこに２人にらみ合ってるみたい｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:05.29,00:09:09.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾀｽﾞﾅ)あ？ よく見えんな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.34,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No los veo bien.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.12,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Cuál es Kakashi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:09.30,00:09:12.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,どっちが カカシ先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.56,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Se movieron!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:12.30,00:09:14.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ 動いた！
Dialogue: 0,00:09:18.31,00:09:19.82,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:09:19.82,00:09:22.32,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.50,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Lo siento, Naruto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:28.84,00:09:32.34,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい ナルト君｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.45,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Todavía no puedo morir.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:38.86,00:09:42.36,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(白)僕は まだ死ねません｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:42.36,00:09:52.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:56.67,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,¿Este es mi fin?
Dialogue: 0,00:09:55.39,00:09:58.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)《ここまでか…》
Dialogue: 0,00:09:58.39,00:10:00.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)うあ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:10:11.42,00:10:14.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ！(ﾀｽﾞﾅ)何じゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.78,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Qué pasó?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:43.48,00:10:45.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)あぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.36,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Zabuza-san…
Dialogue: 0,00:11:11.47,00:11:14.98,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(白)再不斬さん…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:11:14.98,00:11:16.98,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)あ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:19.61,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Decías que solo veías\Nmuerte en mi futuro?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:16.98,00:11:19.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)俺様の未来が死だと？
Dialogue: 0,00:11:19.99,00:11:21.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,フフフ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:25.62,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Volviste a equivocarte, Kakashi.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:21.99,00:11:26.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,また外れたな カカシ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:11:29.54,00:11:33.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾂﾅﾐ)ダメよ １人で橋に行くなんて！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:32.83,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡No puedes! No irás al puente solo.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:35.05,00:11:39.05,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,町じゅう回ったけど誰も一緒に来てくれないんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:39.63,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Hice una ronda por la ciudad,\Npero nadie quiere venir conmigo.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:39.05,00:11:41.99,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,しょうがないよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.20,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No tengo otra opción.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:41.99,00:11:44.50,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾂﾅﾐ)だからって…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:44.67,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Pero…
Dialogue: 0,00:11:54.52,00:11:59.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾂﾅﾐ)待って！あなたは まだ子どもなのよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:59.06,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Espera! Todavía eres un niño.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:59.03,00:12:01.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)僕は まだ子どもだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:01.86,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Sí, soy un niño,
Dialogue: 0,00:12:01.53,00:12:05.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,戦うことがどういうことかは知ってるよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:05.53,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,pero sé lo que significa pelear.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:05.54,00:12:09.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,僕は父ちゃんの息子だから｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.23,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Porque soy el hijo de papá.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:14.06,00:12:16.06,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾂﾅﾐ)《あなた…》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:15.90,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Cariño…
Dialogue: 0,00:12:18.07,00:12:20.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾂﾅﾐ)待ちなさい イナリ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:20.68,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Espera, Inari!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:20.57,00:12:22.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾅﾘ)あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:12:22.57,00:12:24.58,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:12:28.59,00:12:32.09,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あいつ どこへ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.33,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,¿Dónde se metió?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:32.09,00:12:35.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《よく見たら いつの間にか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:37.46,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Ahora veo que la niebla se dispersó.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:35.10,00:12:38.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,霧が晴れてきてるってばよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:12:38.11,00:12:41.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ん？ あそこか！》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.63,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,¿Está ahí?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:45.55,00:12:54.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:12:54.57,00:12:59.08,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ど… どういうことだってばよこれ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:58.83,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Qué significa esto?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:59.08,00:13:04.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:13:04.59,00:13:08.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾀｽﾞﾅ)あれは お面の少年｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:08.03,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Es el chico de la máscara.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:08.60,00:13:13.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)再不斬をかばって飛び込んでくるとは｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:12.75,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Se interpuso\Npara proteger a Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:18.12,00:13:23.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)《この子 もう死んでる》
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:22.59,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Ya está muerto.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:23.63,00:13:28.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)フフフ… 見事だ 白｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.11,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Bien hecho, Haku.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:30.64,00:13:34.15,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)テヤ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.05,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Kakashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:34.15,00:13:36.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,カカシ先生！
Dialogue: 0,00:13:36.16,00:13:39.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)《この子ごと俺を斬るつもりか!?》
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:39.25,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,¿Piensa atacar a través de este chico?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:39.66,00:13:44.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)全く俺は よくよくいい拾い物をしたもんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:44.23,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Tuve suerte de encontrar\Nalgo tan bueno!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:44.10,00:13:49.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,最後の最後で こんなチャンスを与えてくれるとはな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:49.19,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Al final me dio una gran oportunidad.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:56.63,00:13:59.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)＜白 残念だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.43,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Lo siento, Haku.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:59.63,00:14:04.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,こよいかぎり俺は水の国を捨てる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:04.14,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Esta noche renegaré del País del Agua.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:04.14,00:14:09.65,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,しかし 必ず俺は この国に帰ってくる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:09.75,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Pero te aseguro que regresaré.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:09.65,00:14:12.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,この国を手中に入れてみせる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:12.95,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Un día controlaré este país.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:12.66,00:14:16.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そのために必要なのは慰めや励ましや
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:20.17,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Para eso no necesito\Npalabras vacías de consuelo.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:16.67,00:14:20.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何の役にも立たないことばじゃない｡
Dialogue: 0,00:14:20.18,00:14:23.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,本当に必要なのは…＞(白)＜分かっています｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.37,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Lo que necesito…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:25.36,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Lo sé, no te preocupes.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:23.68,00:14:27.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,安心してください僕は 再不斬さんの武器です｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:27.77,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Soy tu arma.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:27.69,00:14:30.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,言いつけを守るただの道具として
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:32.57,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Soy una simple herramienta\Nque obedece tus órdenes sin rechistar.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:30.70,00:14:33.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,おそばに置いてください＞
Dialogue: 0,00:14:34.70,00:14:37.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)＜いい子だ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:37.01,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Buen chico.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:43.66,00:14:46.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)トリャ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:45.33,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Toma esto!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:47.66,00:14:49.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)テイ！
Dialogue: 0,00:14:53.68,00:14:55.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)フフフ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:57.85,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Pudiste moverte porque Haku murió?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:55.68,00:14:59.19,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,白が死んで動けたのか｡
Dialogue: 0,00:14:59.19,00:15:01.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,許せねえ｡(ｶｶｼ)ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.56,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡No te lo perdonaré!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:03.77,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Quédate ahí, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:01.69,00:15:04.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前は そこで見ているんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:04.20,00:15:14.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:15:24.24,00:15:25.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:30.13,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Esta es mi pelea.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:25.74,00:15:27.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)こいつは…
Dialogue: 0,00:15:27.74,00:15:30.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺の戦いだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:34.76,00:15:36.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:36.09,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:36.76,00:15:40.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト！ 無事だったのね！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:40.13,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Naruto! ¿Estás bien?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:40.70,00:15:43.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《サクラちゃん》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.54,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Sakura-chan…
Dialogue: 0,00:15:43.71,00:15:46.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ君は？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.35,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Y Sasuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:48.72,00:15:52.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト… サスケ君は どこなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:52.53,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Dónde está Sasuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:52.73,00:15:54.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,う…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:16:01.75,00:16:04.25,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)サクラ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.07,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Sakura…
Dialogue: 0,00:16:04.25,00:16:09.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)カカシ！よそ見してる暇はねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:07.60,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Kakashi, no puedes permitirte\Nmirar hacia otro lado!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:09.76,00:16:11.26,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,おっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:16:11.26,00:16:15.27,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,わしも一緒に行こう そうすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.27,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Iré contigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.74,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Así no incumplirás\Nlo que dijo tu maestro.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:15.27,00:16:19.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,先生の言いつけを破ったことにはならんじゃろう｡
Dialogue: 0,00:16:19.28,00:16:21.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:20.34,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Bien.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:34.31,00:16:36.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.25,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Sasuke…
Dialogue: 0,00:16:42.76,00:16:44.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,はっ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:16:50.28,00:16:52.28,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,はぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:16:52.28,00:17:02.29,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:17:11.82,00:17:13.82,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,冷たい…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.76,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Está frío.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:17.36,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Esto no es un genjutsu, ¿verdad?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:13.82,00:17:18.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,これはもう幻術じゃないのね｡
Dialogue: 0,00:17:18.33,00:17:22.84,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,わしの前だからって気にすることはない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.63,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No te preocupes por mí.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:22.84,00:17:27.35,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,こういうときは素直に泣いたらええ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:26.63,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,En estos momentos es mejor llorar.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:34.87,00:17:39.88,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,私 いつも忍者学校のテストで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:41.79,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Yo siempre sacaba puntuaciones\Nperfectas en los exámenes de la academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:49.63,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Recuerdo las más de 100 directrices\Nde los shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:53.23,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Siempre escribía la respuesta\Ncon orgullo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:57.63,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,En un examen\Nme encontré con esta pregunta:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:04.14,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,"Escribe la vigésimo quinta directriz\Nde los shinobi".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:09.35,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Y yo respondí, como siempre.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:21.19,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,"Un shinobi no debe mostrar sus\Nemociones bajo ninguna circunstancia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:27.60,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,La misión es su prioridad, y jamás\Ndebe dejar que vean sus lágrimas".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:40.44,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,¿Así son los shinobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:44.05,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Es atroz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:46.85,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:18.53,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,¿Por qué no puedo seguirle el ritmo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.32,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¡Maldita sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:41.64,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Desgraciado…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.91,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,En ese estado no puedes vencerme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:56.32,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Qué?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:20:01.79,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No sabes lo que es la fuerza de verdad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:10.46,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Veamos qué ocurrió aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:20.14,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Adiós, diablo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:49.37,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Incapacité tus dos brazos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.14,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No podrás formar sellos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:05.08,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Vaya, vaya, te está dando una paliza.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:11.05,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Me decepcionas, Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,null,null,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,点 取ってた｡
Dialogue: 0,00:17:42.81,00:17:45.32,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,null,null,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,以上もある忍の心得を全部覚えてて
Dialogue: 0,00:17:49.83,00:17:53.84,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,いつも得意げに答えを書いてた｡
Dialogue: 0,00:17:53.84,00:17:58.85,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ある日のテストでこんな問題が出たの｡
Dialogue: 0,null,null,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,項を答えよ｣って｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:04.36,00:18:07.36,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それで あたしはいつものように
Dialogue: 0,00:18:07.36,00:18:10.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,その答えを書いたわ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:14.88,00:18:18.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,｢忍はどのような状況においても
Dialogue: 0,00:18:18.89,00:18:21.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,感情を表に出すべからず｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:21.39,00:18:23.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,任務を第一とし
Dialogue: 0,00:18:23.40,00:18:28.40,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,何事にも涙を見せぬ心を持つべし｣って｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:31.91,00:18:36.42,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(泣き声)
Dialogue: 0,00:18:36.42,00:18:40.43,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾀｽﾞﾅ)《これが…これが忍というものか｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:40.43,00:18:44.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ… あまりにもつらい》
Dialogue: 0,00:18:44.87,00:18:47.88,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ君…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:47.88,00:18:57.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(泣き声)
Dialogue: 0,00:19:06.41,00:19:09.92,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:09.92,00:19:13.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:13.93,00:19:15.93,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,どうしてだ？
Dialogue: 0,00:19:15.93,00:19:18.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜ ついていけない？
Dialogue: 0,00:19:20.94,00:19:22.95,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)くっそ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:19:22.95,00:19:32.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:19:38.98,00:19:41.48,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)くっそ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:19:41.48,00:19:44.49,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,デヤ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:19:44.49,00:19:47.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,フッ！
Dialogue: 0,00:19:47.00,00:19:49.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:51.50,00:19:55.01,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)今のお前では俺には勝てないよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:55.01,00:19:57.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(再不斬)何だと？
Dialogue: 0,00:19:57.02,00:19:59.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)お前は気付いていない｡
Dialogue: 0,00:19:59.02,00:20:02.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,本当の強さってやつを｡
Dialogue: 0,00:20:06.03,00:20:11.04,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男)フッフフフ…さ～て どうなったか｡
Dialogue: 0,00:20:17.06,00:20:20.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)さよならだ 鬼人よ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:20:29.08,00:20:30.58,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)なっ!?
Dialogue: 0,00:20:46.55,00:20:50.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)これで両腕が使えなくなったな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:20:50.56,00:20:53.06,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,印も結べないぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:20:55.57,00:20:57.57,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)ん？
Dialogue: 0,00:21:01.08,00:21:05.58,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男)おうおう 派手にやられやがって｡
Dialogue: 0,00:21:07.59,00:21:11.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾞﾄｰ)がっかりだよ 再不斬｡
Dialogue: 0,00:21:57.16,00:22:02.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬(ｴﾝﾃﾞｨﾝｸﾞﾃｰﾏ)
Dialogue: 0,00:22:02.17,00:22:08.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:22:08.61,00:22:10.62,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Cultivate your hunger
Dialogue: 0,00:22:10.62,00:22:12.12,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ before you idealize
Dialogue: 0,00:22:12.12,00:22:14.12,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Motivate your anger to
Dialogue: 0,00:22:14.12,00:22:15.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ make them realize
Dialogue: 0,00:22:15.63,00:22:17.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Climbing the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:17.63,00:22:19.13,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Never coming down？
Dialogue: 0,00:22:19.13,00:22:21.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Break in to the contents.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:21.14,00:22:23.14,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Never falling down
Dialogue: 0,00:22:23.14,00:22:26.15,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:22:26.15,00:22:29.15,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ My knee is still shakinglike I was twelve
Dialogue: 0,00:22:29.15,00:22:32.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Sneaking out the class roomby the back door
Dialogue: 0,00:22:32.66,00:22:36.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ A man railed at me twicebut I didn't care
Dialogue: 0,00:22:36.17,00:22:38.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Waiting is wasting
Dialogue: 0,00:22:38.17,00:22:40.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ for people like me
Dialogue: 0,00:22:40.18,00:22:43.18,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Don't try to live so wise.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:43.18,00:22:46.19,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Don't crycoz you're so right.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:46.19,00:22:50.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Don't dry withfakes or fears.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:50.20,00:22:54.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Coz you will hate yourselfin the end.
Dialogue: 0,00:22:54.20,00:23:02.72,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:23:02.72,00:23:06.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Don't try to live so wise.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:06.16,00:23:09.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Don't crycoz you're so right.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:09.67,00:23:12.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Don't dry withfakes or fears.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:12.67,00:23:16.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Coz you will hate yourselfin the end.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:16.68,00:23:19.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Don't try to live so wise.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:19.69,00:23:21.69,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Don't cry coz
Dialogue: 0,00:23:21.69,00:23:23.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ you're so right.
Dialogue: 0,00:23:23.70,00:23:25.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ Don't dry
Dialogue: 0,00:23:28.20,00:23:33.72,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,〈あぁ… てめぇ何やってんだってばよ こら！
Dialogue: 0,00:23:33.72,00:23:36.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前も何とか言えよ 再不斬！
Dialogue: 0,00:23:36.22,00:23:38.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,仲間だったんだろ!?
Dialogue: 0,00:23:38.22,00:23:40.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ずっと…ずっと一緒だったんだろ!?
Dialogue: 0,00:23:40.73,00:23:44.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あいつは お前のことホントに好きだったんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,00:23:44.24,00:23:49.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それなのに… 本当にお前は何とも思わねえのかよ！〉
Dialogue: 0,00:23:47.34,00:23:50.71,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾅﾚｰｼｮﾝ)＜帝光中学校バスケットボール部
Dialogue: 0,00:23:50.71,00:23:52.45,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,部員数は100を超え
Dialogue: 0,00:23:52.45,00:23:56.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,全中三連覇を誇る 超 強豪校
Dialogue: 0,00:23:56.22,00:24:00.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,その輝かしい歴史の中でも特に最強と呼ばれ
Dialogue: 0,00:24:00.70,00:24:05.31,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,無敗を誇った10年に１人の天才が５人同時にいた世代は
Dialogue: 0,00:24:05.31,00:24:08.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,｢キセキの世代｣と言われている
